<!-- ABOUTME: Footer colophon — copyright, RSS, GitHub, and social links. -->
<!-- ABOUTME: Subscribe lives at /subscribe; this footer stays a thin one-line colophon. -->
---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer class="mt-24 px-6 pb-12">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-[--width-wide]">
